race.description: The Prince Of Merewether Hotel Hcp (Bm64)
race.comment: ORTHIE'S BOYS (5) drops in grade after a solid effort at Randwick where he wasn't beaten far. Easier this time and he maps for a lovely trail behind the speed. Expecting him to prove hard to hold out. OLLIE'S SECRET (13) has sharp early toe and will spear across to make his own luck on speed. Rock-hard fit now and will give backers a big sight if left alone up front. SURREAL I AM (6) impressed here last time with a strong finish. Keeps improving and must be respected. ALL HUNKY DORY (1) was consistent last time in and can go well fresh.
